The Claude backend options control account selection, session metadata, non-interactive execution, and branch workflows. @code{ai-agent-claude-accounts} is an alist of account names to Claude configuration directories, and @code{ai-agent-claude-account-file} stores the selected account across Emacs sessions. Use @code{ai-agent-claude-select-account} or the account infix in @code{ai-agent-menu} to switch accounts before starting a new session.

Status and usage polling are controlled by integer intervals. @code{ai-agent-claude-status-interval} defaults to @samp{5} seconds and reads status JSON emitted by the bundled statusline script. @code{ai-agent-claude-usage-interval} defaults to @samp{300} seconds and backs off up to @code{ai-agent-claude-usage-max-interval}, which defaults to @samp{900} seconds.

Batch execution options are passed to @samp{claude -p}. @code{ai-agent-claude-batch-permission-mode} defaults to @samp{"auto"}, @code{ai-agent-claude-batch-max-turns} defaults to @samp{30}, and the allowed tool, model, and appended-system-prompt options let you narrow or expand what non-interactive Claude tasks may do.

Branch and buffer safety options default conservatively. @code{ai-agent-claude-warn-kill-with-branches} defaults to @code{t} and warns before killing a session that belongs to a branch tree. @code{ai-agent-claude-fork-worktree-directory} defaults to a cache directory so isolated branch worktrees do not interfere with cloud sync. @code{ai-agent-claude-handoff-file} defaults to a file in @code{temporary-file-directory}.

Claude hook setup is explicit. @code{ai-agent-claude-settings-file} names the settings file updated by @code{ai-agent-claude-setup-config} and the individual ensure commands. @code{ai-agent-claude-hook-wrapper} points to the upstream @samp{claude-code} hook wrapper, while @code{ai-agent-claude-statusline-script} points to the bundled statusline helper. @code{ai-agent-claude-status-directory} controls where the helper writes per-buffer status JSON files. Loading the backend does not modify Claude Code configuration.

@node Codex backend
@section Codex backend

@vindex ai-agent-codex-handoff-file
